msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.66"
msgid "‘makkhī khomhi paḷāsī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
