msgctxt "mn15:7.81"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.82"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi thaddho atimānī’ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.83"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.84"
msgid "‘thaddho khomhi atimānī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.85"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.86"
msgid "‘atthaddho khomhi anatimānī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (15) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.100, sc69
msgctxt "mn15:7.87"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.88"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī’ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn15:7.89"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that "

msgctxt "mn15:7.90"
msgid "‘sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī khomhi ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
msgstr "they are attached to their own views, holding them tight, and refusing to let go. Then they should make an effort to give up those bad, unskillful qualities. "

msgctxt "mn15:7.91"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti: "
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that "

msgctxt "mn15:7.92"
msgid "‘asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī khomhi anādhānaggāhī suppaṭinissaggī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (16) "
msgstr "they’re not attached to their own views, holding them tight, but let them go easily. Then they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya8, sc70
msgctxt "mn15:8.1"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā sabbesaṃyeva imesaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant sees that they haven’t given up all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should make an effort to give them all up. "

msgctxt "mn15:8.2"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme pahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ, ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. "
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant sees that they have given up all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc71
msgctxt "mn15:8.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, itthī vā puriso vā, daharo yuvā maṇḍanajātiko, ādāse vā parisuddhe pariyodāte, acche vā udakapatte, sakaṃ mukhanimittaṃ paccavekkhamāno, sace tattha passati rajaṃ vā aṅgaṇaṃ vā, tasseva rajassa vā aṅgaṇassa vā pahānāya vāyamati; "
msgstr "Suppose there was a woman or man who was young, youthful, and fond of adornments, and they check their own reflection in a clean bright mirror or a clear bowl of water. If they see any dirt or blemish there, they’d try to remove it. "

msgctxt "mn15:8.4"
msgid "no ce tattha passati rajaṃ vā aṅgaṇaṃ vā, teneva attamano hoti: "
msgstr "But if they don’t see any dirt or blemish there, they’re happy, thinking: "

msgctxt "mn15:8.5"
msgid "‘lābhā vata me, parisuddhaṃ vata me’ti. "
msgstr "‘How fortunate that I’m clean!’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn15:8.6"
msgid "Evameva kho, āvuso, sace bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā sabbesaṃyeva imesaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
msgstr "In the same way, suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant sees that they haven’t given up all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should make an effort to give them all up. "

msgctxt "mn15:8.7"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme pahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ, ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesū”ti. "
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant sees that they have given up all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc72
msgctxt "mn15:8.8"
msgid "Idamavocāyasmā mahāmoggallāno. "
msgstr "This is what Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said. "

msgctxt "mn15:8.9"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
